METHODS

Thai Tuan:


Viet Tien:
    General Projects
    + Using the experience specialised in UI/UX to redesign and edit the details of the UI's website.
    + using a method inserting frames containing <information cards> to a <div> that is scrollable based on overflow x.
        .container {
            width: {limited-scale};
            height: 100%;
        }
        div {
            width: 100%; (overflow by the limited scale in width)
            overflow-x: scroll;
        }
    + Hide scrollbar
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
    
    My information cards
    + Using basic methods to design a card.
    + creative: 
        - QR Code
        - new layout
        - svg icon

Others:
    + They learn the knowledge from W3schoool web to implement their information cards.
    + Some contributors struggled with the layouts, so there was time-consuming problems happening during their projects.
    + There are many interesting initiatives in building personal cards, like flipping, gradient, ...
